{"text_id":174789,"tokens":["The"," Earth"," is"," constantly"," changing"," and"," moving"," in"," predictable"," patterns"," and"," cycles","."," The"," water"," cycle"," and"," nutrient"," cycles"," (","carbon",","," nitrogen",","," oxygen",","," sulfur",","," etc",".)"," are"," Earth","'","s"," metabolism","."," The"," Homo"," sapiens"," component"," of"," Earth","'","s"," metabolism"," is"," toxic"," to"," the"," other"," components"," of"," the"," metabolism","."," These"," problems"," can"," be"," addressed"," in"," the"," design"," of"," human"," settlements",","," cities",","," and"," agriculture","."," The"," elements"," of"," the"," Earth"," are"," in"," a"," constant"," state"," of"," motion"," and"," change","."," The"," continents"," are"," slowly"," moving"," on"," the"," plates"," that"," make"," up"," the"," Earth","'","s"," crust","."," Ocean"," currents"," circulate"," water"," around"," the"," globe","."," Nutrients"," are"," constantly"," being"," recycled"," in"," the"," carbon",","," nitrogen",","," oxygen",","," sulfur",","," and"," water"," cycles","."," This"," circulation"," of"," elements"," is"," what"," some"," eco","logists"," call"," metabolism","."," Metabolism"," of"," the"," Earth"," is"," very"," complex","."," Many"," of"," these"," cycles"," are"," interrelated","."," For"," example",","," the"," carbon"," cycle"," and"," the"," nitrogen"," cycle"," are"," inextrica","bly"," linked","."," In"," addition",","," there"," are"," many"," cycles"," within"," cycles",","," such"," as"," the"," calcium"," cycle"," (","calcium"," is"," part"," of"," the"," carbon"," cycle",")."," The"," carbon"," cycle"," is"," one"," of"," the"," most"," important"," processes"," of"," Earth"," metabolism","."," Carbon"," is"," the"," building"," block"," of"," all"," living"," things","."," Carbon"," is"," found"," in"," the"," air"," in"," the"," form"," of"," carbon"," dioxide"," (","CO","2",")."," Plants"," absorb"," carbon"," dioxide"," from"," the"," air"," and"," use"," it"," as"," a"," raw"," material"," for"," photosynthesis","."," Plants"," then"," give"," off"," oxygen"," as"," a"," byproduct"," of"," photosynthesis","."," This"," process"," is"," so"," important"," to"," human"," life"," that"," it"," is"," often"," described"," as"," the"," \"","lungs"," of"," the"," Earth",".\""," Unfortunately",","," humans"," are"," affecting"," this"," cycle"," in"," ways"," that"," are"," detrimental"," to"," our"," health","."," Carbon"," dioxide"," is"," a"," greenhouse"," gas","."," As"," the"," amount"," of"," carbon"," dioxide"," in"," the"," atmosphere"," rises",","," so"," does"," the"," temperature","."," In"," addition",","," the"," higher"," concentration"," of"," carbon"," dioxide"," in"," the"," atmosphere"," can"," lower"," the"," nutritional"," value"," of"," plants","."," The"," water"," cycle",","," or"," hydrologic"," cycle",","," is"," the"," process"," by"," which"," water"," is"," recycled","."," Water"," is"," continually"," moving"," from"," one"," place"," to"," another"," as"," it"," is"," stored"," and"," transferred"," on",","," above",","," and"," below"," the"," surface"," of"," the"," Earth","."," The"," water"," cycle"," involves"," water"," that"," is"," liquid",","," solid"," (","ice","),"," and"," gas"," (","water"," vapor",")."," The"," water"," cycle"," begins"," when"," water"," from"," the"," ocean"," is"," heated"," by"," the"," sun"," and"," evapor","ates","."," The"," water"," vapor"," is"," carried"," by"," winds"," to"," other"," locations"," and"," eventually"," cond","enses"," to"," form"," clouds","."," The"," water"," in"," the"," clouds"," falls"," back"," to"," Earth"," as"," precipitation",","," such"," as"," rain"," and"," snow","."," Some"," of"," this"," precipitation"," falls"," on"," the"," ocean"," and"," some"," falls"," on"," land","."," The"," water"," on"," the"," land"," is"," either"," used"," by"," plants"," or"," flows"," into"," rivers"," and"," streams"," and"," eventually"," finds"," its"," way"," back"," to"," the"," ocean","."," The"," nitrogen"," cycle"," is"," a"," cycle"," of"," nitrogen"," through"," the"," atmosphere",","," soil",","," plants",","," animals",","," and"," back"," into"," the"," atmosphere","."," This"," cycle"," is"," dependent"," upon"," many"," different"," factors","."," Nitrogen"," is"," a"," component"," of"," the"," air",","," water",","," soil",","," and"," all"," living"," things","."," The"," nitrogen"," cycle"," is"," dependent"," upon"," the"," process"," of"," nitrogen"," fixation","."," Nitrogen"," is"," a"," component"," of"," the"," atmosphere"," but"," plants"," cannot"," use"," it"," in"," this"," form","."," Bacteria"," in"," the"," soil"," and"," water"," fix"," the"," nitrogen"," by"," converting"," it"," into"," a"," form"," that"," plants"," can"," use","."," Other"," bacteria"," then"," decompose"," dead"," plants"," and"," animals","."," Some"," of"," this"," nitrogen"," is"," released"," back"," into"," the"," air","."," Some"," is"," used"," by"," other"," plants"," and"," animals","."," As"," the"," living"," things"," die",","," the"," nitrogen"," is"," released"," back"," into"," the"," soil"," and"," the"," cycle"," begins"," again","."," The"," Homo"," sapiens"," component"," of"," Earth","'","s"," metabolism"," is"," toxic"," to"," the"," other"," components"," of"," the"," metabolism","."," For"," example",","," carbon"," dioxide"," levels"," have"," increased"," from"," ","2","8","0"," ppm"," to"," ","4","0","0"," ppm"," since"," ","1","7","5","0","."," Nit","rous"," oxide"," levels"," are"," also"," increasing","."," The"," increasing"," carbon"," dioxide"," levels"," have"," led"," to"," warmer"," temperatures","."," The"," temperature"," has"," increased"," by"," .","6"," degrees"," Celsius"," since"," ","1","9","5","0","."," This"," has"," had"," a"," detrimental"," effect"," on"," the"," Earth","'","s"," metabolism","."," The"," warmer"," temperat